Description: Hydrate and protect lips naturally with this nourishing 100% natural lip balm. This healing balm is loaded with 5 pure oils that are rich in vitamins and essential fatty acids, to nourish, condition and soften lips. * Kokum Butter, one of nature's richest emollients, soothes and moisturizes dry lips and seals in hydration.* Shea Butter lends extra moisturizing and nourishing feast to the lips* Macadamia, Sunflower and Sweet Almond form a nourishing and hydrating base while protecting from the sun.* Mint oil refreshes.Deliberately formulated to be very slightly aromatic and also coats thin and not sticky like commercial vaselin based balms. Instructions: Apply balm liberally to your lips as often as needed, particularly in dry, cold or windy conditions. Your best companion, take this lip balm anywhere and use it as often as you like. Remember that you are absorbing or swallowing at least 60 percent of the chemicals and non-natural oils you slather on your lips all day long. Title: Instantly Ageless Wrinkle Free Eye Bag/Face Uplifting Cream Trial Pack of 5(1.5 ml)
Description: Let’s dive in…Aging is a natural process that everyone goes through, and the skin is usually one of the first parts of the body to display signs of it. Wrinkles, lines and a general loss of firmness in the skin around the face are perhaps the most visibly notable signs of aging, and appear on every person at one point or another.Jeunesse Instantly Ageless is a product that looks to combine two of these processes, offering a beauty product available over the counter that claims to have results as good as anti-aging surgical procedures such as Botox (some consider it the “botox in a box” product).What is Instantly Ageless?Instantly Ageless is a micro-cream created specifically to combat the signs of aging on the skin of the face. As the most notable problem areas for wrinkles, lines, puffiness, and general wear and tear, our faces are susceptible to all sorts of damage that can accelerate the aging process of the skin.Instantly Ageless can reduce the signs of aging almost instantly. It has even been claimed to be a great and natural alternative to Botox, which freezes the muscles in the face to act as an anti-aging formula for the skin, producing the same results, yet without the need for chemical injections.(*)Results may vary from person to personHow Does Instantly Ageless Work?The credit for the effectiveness of this serum goes to the active ingredients. The main ingredient in question is the peptide Argireline, which happens to have a striking similarity to how Botox works on the skin.Facial muscles are almost instantly relaxed after the cream is applied, which causes the skin to react in a way much akin to Botox. Skin is soothed and softened in a matter of minutes, which means that any appearance of wrinkles lines and other signs of aging in the skin are improved almost immediately.The combination of the other active ingredients also has strong anti-aging properties, including helping to improve the elasticity of the skin, as well as reducing the size and appearance of pores, which are other contributing factors to the appearance of aged skin.Instructions for Instantly AgelessAs it is no simple moisturizer or anti-wrinkle cream, Instantly Ageless requires a special application to ensure it is successful in its treatment. Although this is by no means a complex matter, and can be incorporated into most daily applications of other beauty products.1 – FOREHEAD APPLICATIONApply the cream across your whole forehead, not just on the wrinkle lines.2 – EYEBROW RejuvenationJust dab it above your eyebrow line for a quick “brow lift”3 – EYE LIDSApply cream from the crease of your eye to the bottom of your eye brow (do not apply it on your eye lid)4 – UNDER EYE DARK CIRCLES & LAUGH LINESGently apply cream under your eye on the dark circles, and also on your laugh lines.5 – PORES APPLICATIONApply cream as needed on the target areas.With a product sounding almost too good to be true, one question will always arise with beauty products – is it safe to use? Are there any side effects consumers should be aware of?So far the answer appears to be a resounding no for the most part. There are some risks that come with the product, but this is in the same way that thousands of everyday products can provide a certain risk if not used properly.The product should always be avoided with eye contact, which like many beauty products, is a given. Another common cause of irritation from the product is if you are allergic to any of the ingredients or just have sensitive skin towards the product.Again, these are not problems the average consumer needs to concern themselves with, as it is very uncommon among most buyers.Are There Side Effects?None have been noted to date, making it completely safe and side-effect free. Again, allergies towards certain components can cause side-effects, but this is completely determined by the individual and not the product itself.Should this occur, consult your doctor as you would with any sort of allergic reaction. The same should be done if any irritations are causes, or if the skin reddens, as this could be your skin taking a negative reaction to something inside the product.This means that there are absolutely no dangers when using instantly ageless.With a rep for being so effective, most would assume that it comes with some sort of catch. That doesn’t appear to be the case for Instantly Ageless, which has not reports of adverse side-effects or any type of safety concerns.

Title: Instantly Ageless Wrinkleless Eye Bag and Face Uplifting Cream Pack of 50
Description: Let’s dive in…Aging is a natural process that everyone goes through, and the skin is usually one of the first parts of the body to display signs of it. Wrinkles, lines and a general loss of firmness in the skin around the face are perhaps the most visibly notable signs of aging, and appear on every person at one point or another.Jeunesse Instantly Ageless is a product that looks to combine two of these processes, offering a beauty product available over the counter that claims to have results as good as anti-aging surgical procedures such as Botox (some consider it the “botox in a box” product).What is Instantly Ageless?Instantly Ageless is a micro-cream created specifically to combat the signs of aging on the skin of the face. As the most notable problem areas for wrinkles, lines, puffiness, and general wear and tear, our faces are susceptible to all sorts of damage that can accelerate the aging process of the skin.Instantly Ageless can reduce the signs of aging almost instantly. It has even been claimed to be a great and natural alternative to Botox, which freezes the muscles in the face to act as an anti-aging formula for the skin, producing the same results, yet without the need for chemical injections.(*)Results may vary from person to personHow Does Instantly Ageless Work?The credit for the effectiveness of this serum goes to the active ingredients. The main ingredient in question is the peptide Argireline, which happens to have a striking similarity to how Botox works on the skin.Facial muscles are almost instantly relaxed after the cream is applied, which causes the skin to react in a way much akin to Botox. Skin is soothed and softened in a matter of minutes, which means that any appearance of wrinkles lines and other signs of aging in the skin are improved almost immediately.The combination of the other active ingredients also has strong anti-aging properties, including helping to improve the elasticity of the skin, as well as reducing the size and appearance of pores, which are other contributing factors to the appearance of aged skin.Instructions for Instantly AgelessAs it is no simple moisturizer or anti-wrinkle cream, Instantly Ageless requires a special application to ensure it is successful in its treatment. Although this is by no means a complex matter, and can be incorporated into most daily applications of other beauty products.1 – FOREHEAD APPLICATIONApply the cream across your whole forehead, not just on the wrinkle lines.2 – EYEBROW RejuvenationJust dab it above your eyebrow line for a quick “brow lift”3 – EYE LIDSApply cream from the crease of your eye to the bottom of your eye brow (do not apply it on your eye lid)4 – UNDER EYE DARK CIRCLES & LAUGH LINESGently apply cream under your eye on the dark circles, and also on your laugh lines.5 – PORES APPLICATIONApply cream as needed on the target areas.With a product sounding almost too good to be true, one question will always arise with beauty products – is it safe to use? Are there any side effects consumers should be aware of?So far the answer appears to be a resounding no for the most part. There are some risks that come with the product, but this is in the same way that thousands of everyday products can provide a certain risk if not used properly.The product should always be avoided with eye contact, which like many beauty products, is a given. Another common cause of irritation from the product is if you are allergic to any of the ingredients or just have sensitive skin towards the product.Again, these are not problems the average consumer needs to concern themselves with, as it is very uncommon among most buyers.Are There Side Effects?None have been noted to date, making it completely safe and side-effect free. Again, allergies towards certain components can cause side-effects, but this is completely determined by the individual and not the product itself.Should this occur, consult your doctor as you would with any sort of allergic reaction. The same should be done if any irritations are causes, or if the skin reddens, as this could be your skin taking a negative reaction to something inside the product.This means that there are absolutely no dangers when using instantly ageless.With a rep for being so effective, most would assume that it comes with some sort of catch. That doesn’t appear to be the case for Instantly Ageless, which has not reports of adverse side-effects or any type of safety concerns.
